data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the beautiful city of Port St Lucie! This stunning single-family home boasts an impressive five bedrooms, perfect for accommodating a growing family or hosting guests. At first glance  The split floor plan offers privacy and convenience. This 2-story home provides a comfortable family room neighboring a very large kitchen. The large kitchen is a chef's delight featuring an abundance of storage with 2 pantries and an island perfect for a large family and hosting gathering events for the upcoming holidays. Whether you're preparing a quick breakfast or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen is sure to impress. Easy entrance into an also large dining area with more than enough space to create everlasting memories with family and friends. The main floor also features a half bathroom with a very large bedroom and walk in closet with in-law suite potential. A conveniently dedicated laundry room and two-car garage provides ample space for your vehicles and additional storage needs. Upstairs, you'll find the remaining bedrooms, each generously sized and flooded with natural light. and a full bathroom. These large bedrooms provide endless possibilities, whether you choose to create a home office, a playroom, or a cozy reading nook. The master bedroom is not only oversized but also features his & her walk-in closets and a big bathroom with a bathtub and stand-up shower. One of the standout features of this home is the dual shed, providing ample space for all your storage needs. Whether you have outdoor equipment, holiday decorations, or simply need a place to store your belongings, these sheds offer the perfect solution. The backyard features lovely shade to enjoy the gorgeous Florida weather as well as a mango tree. The two-story design of this home adds an element of grandeur and allows for a seamless flow between the living spaces. This lovely home sits just in between I-95 and the Florida turnpike for quick access to both major highways. With its convenient location, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Port St Lucie offers a vibrant community with an array of amenities and attractions. From beautiful beaches to championship golf courses, there is something for everyone to enjoy. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this 5-bedroom, single-family home yours for this incredible price!
